column1:
Day Of The Dead Tissue Garland

Day Of The Dead Tissue Garland is the perfect Day of the Dead decorations.
column4:
>Hang these happy skeletons around your room when trying to create a festive Day of the Dead theme. Each alternating color skeleton is approximately eleven (11) inches tall and the entire tissue garland stretches out twelve feet long.

Great for Halloween parties too!

column1:
• Celebrate Dia De Los Muertos with this tissue Day of the Dead Garland.
  • 11.5 Inches x 12 Feet
  • One (1) per package
  • If you are looking for more Day of the Dead hanging decorations check out this package of five Day of the Dead Whirls.
